{"TopicId":221708,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"Question about the latest release notes -For Science!- about \u0022re-rendering clouds edges to improve performance\u0022","CreatedByName":"Mushylog","CreatedById":227298,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T03:52:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mushylog","CreatedById":227298,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T03:52:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022excerpt-releasenotes.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002241.45\u0022 height=\u0022383\u0022 width=\u0022924\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1146578408755699712/1187602145357336596/excerpt-releasenotes.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;hm=97bccda8d3e8bf58c719ce00cea1bb66e63d3d9a37af02919b184e7e6231a9a3\u0026amp;=\u0026amp;format=webp\u0026amp;quality=lossless\u0026amp;width=1016\u0026amp;height=421\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe clouds are now a little less pretty around the flying craft. Before the (great) update, the clouds around the active vessel looked great, no bleeding edges or anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, the weird zone around the vessel is visible again, despite an even more beautiful shadow render for the clouds. So I\u0027m curious:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy was this decision taken? Will we get a better performing rendering system for the clouds? Will this change be permanent, regarding the clouds edges rendering?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cloudsedge4.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.76\u0022 height=\u0022442\u0022 width=\u0022487\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1146578408755699712/1187602145894211594/cloudsedge4.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;hm=5521df5b62bce4d4447752a84d3ff2fb87a56287f8a9122aecc48c0ea3bcb818\u0026amp;=\u0026amp;format=webp\u0026amp;quality=lossless\u0026amp;width=535\u0026amp;height=486\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cloudsedge3.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002253.53\u0022 height=\u0022303\u0022 width=\u0022566\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1146578408755699712/1187602146376552468/cloudsedge3.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;hm=a28ac37e78d9e0de0d066dcd50597c01e5c59bfd46400516cd2a79a053e4e110\u0026amp;=\u0026amp;format=webp\u0026amp;quality=lossless\u0026amp;width=622\u0026amp;height=333\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cloudsedge2.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.51\u0022 height=\u0022701\u0022 width=\u0022421\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1146578408755699712/1187602146938593441/cloudsedge2.png?ex=65977bb0\u0026amp;is=658506b0\u0026amp;hm=57011af66780b5328ac7e87af74719f8afe6cab3e59b87cd6d035d32a71db4e6\u0026amp;=\u0026amp;format=webp\u0026amp;quality=lossless\u0026amp;width=421\u0026amp;height=701\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TROPtastic","CreatedById":211826,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T04:59:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, I\u0027m not sure if this is actually what the patch notes are referring to, or if it\u0027s an unintended side effect of a rendering change. IIRC the dev blog didn\u0027t refer to rendering around aircraft edges.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps try submitting a bug report in the Bug Reports sub forum? Worst case is that they say it\u0027s intended and clarify, best case is that you alert them to a regression.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: instructions are here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2295247635\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/213016-bug-reports-should-be-posted-in-the-ksp2-bug-reports-subforum-linked-in-thread/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:217px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-22T05:05:10Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2023 05:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 22\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by TROPtastic\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}